---
// src/pages/index.astro
// ==========================================
// VETERAN.CORE // DEFAULT ENGLISH HOMEPAGE
// ==========================================
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>VETERAN.CORE // Hardware Expertise & BOM Optimization</title>
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Inter:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

    <style is:inline>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #09090b !important;
        color: #fafafa !important;
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      
      .gveh-header { 
        padding: 25px 5%; 
        display: flex !important;
        justify-content: space-between !important;
        align-items: flex-start !important;
      }

      .gveh-logo-link {
        text-decoration: none !important;
        display: block !important;
        width: 180px !important;
        position: absolute !important;
        top: 25px !important;
        left: 5% !important;
        z-index: 999 !important;
      }

      .gveh-lang-top-btn {
        text-decoration: none !important;
        font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace !important;
        font-size: 12px !important;
        font-weight: 700 !important;
        color: #aaa !important;
        border: 1px solid #333 !important;
        padding: 6px 12px !important;
        border-radius: 4px !important;
        background: transparent !important;
        transition: all 0.3s ease !important;
        position: absolute !important;
        top: 25px !important;
        right: 5% !important;
        z-index: 999 !important;
      }
      .gveh-lang-top-btn:hover {
        color: #f39c12 !important;
        border-color: #f39c12 !important;
      }

      .gveh-hero { 
        max-width: 1200px; 
        margin: 180px auto 60px auto; 
        padding: 0 40px; 
        text-align: center; 
      }
      .gveh-hero h1 { 
        font-size: 3.5rem; 
        font-weight: 700; 
        line-height: 1.2; 
        margin-bottom: 24px; 
        color: #ffffff; 
        letter-spacing: -0.02em; 
      }
      .gveh-hero h1 span { 
        color: #f39c12 !important; 
        font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace !important; 
      }
      .gveh-hero p { 
        font-size: 1.25rem; 
        color: #a1a1aa !important; 
        max-width: 800px; 
        margin: 0 auto; 
        line-height: 1.6; 
      }
      
      .gveh-matrix { 
        max-width: 1200px; 
        margin: 40px auto 180px auto; 
        padding: 0 20px; 
        display: grid; 
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); 
        gap: 24px; 
      }
      .gveh-card { 
        background-color: #141417 !important; 
        border: 1px solid rgba(63, 63, 70, 0.4) !important; 
        padding: 32px; 
        border-radius: 4px; 
      }
      .gveh-card-tag { 
        font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace !important; 
        color: #f39c12 !important; 
        font-size: 0.75rem; 
        margin-bottom: 16px; 
      }
      .gveh-card h2 { 
        font-size: 1.5rem; 
        margin: 0 0 16px 0; 
        color: #ffffff; 
      }
      .gveh-card p { 
        color: #a1a1aa !important; 
        font-size: 0.95rem; 
        line-height: 1.6; 
        margin: 0; 
      }

      .gveh-nav-container {
        position: fixed !important; 
        bottom: 0 !important; 
        left: 50% !important; 
        transform: translateX(-50%) !important;
        padding-bottom: 28px !important; 
        padding-top: 50px !important; 
        z-index: 9999 !important;
        display: flex !important; 
        justify-content: center !important; 
        align-items: center !important; 
        cursor: pointer !important;
      }
      .gveh-hover-pill {
        border: 1px solid rgba(63, 63, 70, 0.2) !important; 
        padding: 8px 24px !important;
        display: flex !important; 
        justify-content: center !important; 
        align-items: center !important; 
        gap: 36px !important; 
        border-radius: 9999px !important;
        opacity: 0.15 !important; 
        transform: translateY(15px) scale(0.98) !important;
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) !important;
        background-color: rgba(20, 20, 23, 0.4) !important; 
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) !important;
      }
      .gveh-nav-container:hover .gveh-hover-pill {
        opacity: 1 !important; 
        transform: translateY(0) scale(1) !important;
        background-color: rgba(24, 24, 27, 0.98) !important;
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px) !important; 
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px) !important;
        border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4) !important;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.7), 0 0 20px rgba(245,158,11,0.15) !important;
      }
      .gveh-nav-item {
        text-decoration: none !important; 
        display: flex !important; 
        flex-direction: column !important;
        align-items: center !important; 
        gap: 3px !important; 
        color: rgba(161, 161, 170, 0.7) !important; 
        transition: all 0.2s ease !important;
      }
      .gveh-nav-text {
        font-size: 10px !important; 
        font-weight: 700 !important; 
        letter-spacing: 0.1em !important;
        text-transform: uppercase !important; 
        font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace !important;
      }
      .gveh-nav-item:hover { 
        color: #f39c12 !important; 
      }
      .gveh-nav-item.active { 
        color: #f39c12 !important; 
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .gveh-logo-link {
          width: 130px !important;
          position: static !important;
          margin: 0 auto 20px auto !important;
          display: block !important;
          top: auto !important;
          left: auto !important;
        }
        .gveh-lang-top-btn {
          position: static !important;
          top: auto !important;
          right: auto !important;
          margin-bottom: 20px !important;
        }
        .gveh-header {
          flex-direction: column !important;
          align-items: center !important;
          padding: 20px 5% !important;
        }
        .gveh-hero { 
          margin: 20px auto 30px auto; 
          padding: 0 20px; 
        }
        .gveh-hero h1 { 
          font-size: 2rem; 
        }
        .gveh-matrix { 
          grid-template-columns: 1fr; 
          margin-bottom: 140px; 
          padding: 0 20px; 
        }
        img {
          max-width: 130px !important;
          height: auto !important;
          margin: 0 auto !important;
          display: block !important;
        }
        h1 {
          text-align: center !important;
          padding-top: 15px !important;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="gveh-header">
      <a href="/" class="gveh-logo-link">
        <img src="/pnds-logo.png" alt="PNDS Panda Hardware Expertise" style="width: 100% !important; height: auto !important;" />
      </a>
      <a href="/zh" class="gveh-lang-top-btn">EN / 中文</a>
    </header>

    <main style="flex: 1;">
      <section class="gveh-hero">
        <h1>Don't Just Buy Components.<br />Source with <span>22 Years</span> of Hardware Expertise.</h1>
        <p>[Coordinate: Shenzhen] Providing independent technical analysis, component optimization, and lifecycle risk mitigation for global engineers.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="gveh-matrix">
        <div class="gveh-card">
          <div class="gveh-card-tag">DOMESTIC VS GLOBAL</div>
          <h2>Domestic vs Global</h2>
          <p>Deep reliability validation, pin-to-pin cross-reference analysis, and transparent alternative options benchmarking tier-1 manufacturers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gveh-card">
          <div class="gveh-card-tag">BOM OPTIMIZATION</div>
          <h2>BOM Optimization</h2>
          <p>Strategic cost reduction without compromising quality. Proactive obsolescence management and resilient supply chain consulting.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gveh-card">
          <div class="gveh-card-tag">ABOUT ME</div>
          <h2>About Me</h2>
          <p>Rooted in Shenzhen since 2004. 22 years of elite hardware engineering experience acting as your clear, uncompromised eyes on the component market.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <div class="gveh-nav-container">
      <div class="gveh-hover-pill">
        <a href="/" class="gveh-nav-item active">
          <svg style="width:18px; height:18px;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"></path></svg>
          <span class="gveh-nav-text">HOME</span>
        </a>
        <div style="width: 1px !important; height: 16px !important; background-color: rgba(63, 63, 70, 0.5) !important;"></div>
        <a href="/bom-hub" class="gveh-nav-item">
          <svg style="width:18px; height:18px;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path></svg>
          <span class="gveh-nav-text">BOM HUB</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>
